# Rust
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock is intentionally committed: this workspace builds release
# binaries (the Tauri desktop app + CLI), so we want fully reproducible CI
# builds. Without the lockfile, CI floats transitive deps to the latest
# semver-compatible versions, which broke the v1.11.1 release when `time`
# 0.3.52 stopped compiling against `cookie` 0.18.1.

